{"tid":1193913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】馬恩國：中国司法改革已較陽光　遊行屬政治抹黑行為","createTime":"2019-06-09T06:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T12:16:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"861c1c5cc2ccfcfdf2969445dbda7960f95f4f3f","tid":1193913,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2892127/org/b0643aae6093ae39d3fd9eb409111e8c.jpg/RHw7ZGdi6xgZ-vHyeP2pgyksVkJ8HLsZQD3gLEA94Cw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2892127%2Forg%2Fb0643aae6093ae39d3fd9eb409111e8c.jpg%2FRHw7ZGdi6xgZ-vHyeP2pgyksVkJ8HLsZQD3gLEA94Cw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=1d70aada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府修訂《逃犯條例》內容備受爭議，香港法學交流基金會主席馬恩國、立法會內務委員會前主席劉健儀、前立法會議員何俊仁及立法會議員范國威今(9日) 出席城市論壇，討論《逃犯條例》修訂。馬恩國表示，中國刑事法已符合七項聯合國的最低人權保障，對於外界認為內地沒有公平審訊，他稱指公開審訊不是聯合國最低的人權保障，認為現時大陸司法改革已較為陽光；何俊仁以維權律師王全璋一案為例，指該案件至今仍沒判證，即使王全璋入獄後亦未有人能夠探獄，反映內地的審訊制度不公的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/338458/逃犯條例-馬恩國-內地司法改革已較陽光-遊行屬政治抹黑行為\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F338458%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%A6%AC%E6%81%A9%E5%9C%8B-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%B7%B2%E8%BC%83%E9%99%BD%E5%85%89-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%AC%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=1d1b7f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/338458/逃犯條例-馬恩國-內地司法改革已較陽光-遊行屬政治抹黑行為</a>"},{"pid":"c0519629eee56d065a1cf394e7b1850c72bcd187","tid":1193913,"uid":117837,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"取消咗澳洲籍未"},{"pid":"5e72848069559c0e9c234759afb47f309e8c5fd0","tid":1193913,"uid":39777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"係論壇兇人誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 